summary: AN ORDINANCE relating to and amending Plat 66 W, Page 159 of the Official Zoning Map of The City of Seattle, Ordinance 86300, to rezone certain property in Tract 4, Morningside Acre Tracts from Duplex Residence High Density (RD 5000) Zone to Multiple Residence Low Density (RM 800) Zone and accepting a Property Use and Development Agreement in connection therewith. (Petition of George C. Pallis, C.F. 289163).
